#

Baked Pork Chops with Garlic and Herbs

40 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickPorkMain Course

Description

Juicy baked pork chops seasoned with aromatic garlic and fresh herbs for a flavorful meal.

Ingredients

  • pork chops: 4 (1-inch thick)
  • garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh rosemary: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • fresh thyme: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
